</span></li><li about="#cite_note-74" id="cite_note-74"><a href="./War#cite_ref-74" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-74" class="mw-reference-text">
<cite class="citation book" about="#mwt232" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book\n","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last1":{"wt":"Fried"},"first1":{"wt":"Marvin Benjamin"},"title":{"wt":"Austro-Hungarian War Aims in the Balkans During World War I"},"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/books?id=ETDtAwAAQBAJ"},"publisher":{"wt":"Palgrave Macmillan"},"publication-date":{"wt":"2014"},"page":{"wt":"4"},"isbn":{"wt":"9781137359018"},"accessdate":{"wt":"2015-08-24"},"quote":{"wt":"War aims are the desired territorial, economic, military or other benefits expected following successful conclusion of a war."},"date":{"wt":"2014-07-01"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBC4">Fried, Marvin Benjamin (2014-07-01). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=ETDtAwAAQBAJ" id="mwBC8"><i id="mwBDA">Austro-Hungarian War Aims in the Balkans During World War I</i></a>. Palgrave Macmillan (published 2014). p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBDE"> </span>4. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwBDI">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBDM"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/9781137359018" title="Special:BookSources/9781137359018" id="mwBDQ">9781137359018</a><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwBDU">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwBDY">2015-08-24</span></span>. <q id="mwBDc">War aims are the desired territorial, economic, military or other benefits expected following successful conclusion of a war.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Austro-Hungarian+War+Aims+in+the+Balkans+During+World+War+I&amp;rft.pages=4&amp;rft.pub=Palgrave+Macmillan&amp;rft.date=2014-07-01&amp;rft.isbn=9781137359018&amp;rft.aulast=Fried&amp;rft.aufirst=Marvin+Benjamin&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DETDtAwAAQBAJ&am