</span></li><li about="#cite_note-75" id="cite_note-75"><a href="./War#cite_ref-75" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-75" class="mw-reference-text">
Welch distinguishes: "tangible goods such as arms, wealth, and – provided they are strategically or economically valuable – territory and resources" from "intangible goods such as credibility and reputation" – <cite class="citation book" about="#mwt235" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book\n","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last1":{"wt":"Welch"},"first1":{"wt":"David A."},"title":{"wt":"Justice and the Genesis of War"},"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/books?id=i2Z5blE1KGoC"},"series":{"wt":"Cambridge Studies in International Relations"},"issue":{"wt":"29"},"publisher":{"wt":"Cambridge University Press"},"publication-date":{"wt":"1995"},"page":{"wt":"17"},"isbn":{"wt":"9780521558686"},"accessdate":{"wt":"2015-08-24"},"date":{"wt":"1995-08-10"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBDo">Welch, David A. (1995-08-10). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=i2Z5blE1KGoC" id="mwBDs"><i id="mwBDw">Justice and the Genesis of War</i></a>. Cambridge Studies in International Relations. Cambridge University Press (published 1995). p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBD0"> </span>17. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwBD4">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBD8"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/9780521558686" title="Special:BookSources/9780521558686" id="mwBEA">9780521558686</a><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwBEE">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwBEI">2015-08-24</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Justice+and+the+Genesis+of+War&amp;rft.series=Cambridge+Studies+in+International+Relations&amp;rft.pages=17&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft.date=1995-08-10&amp;rft.isbn=9780521558686&amp;rft.aulast=Welch&amp;rft.aufirst=David+A.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com