</span></li><li about="#cite_note-76" id="cite_note-76"><a href="./War#cite_ref-76" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-76" class="mw-reference-text">
<cite class="citation book" about="#mwt236" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book\n","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last1":{"wt":"Fried"},"first1":{"wt":"Marvin Benjamin"},"title":{"wt":"Austro-Hungarian War Aims in the Balkans During World War I"},"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/books?id=ETDtAwAAQBAJ"},"publisher":{"wt":"Palgrave Macmillan"},"publication-date":{"wt":"2014"},"page":{"wt":"4"},"isbn":{"wt":"9781137359018"},"accessdate":{"wt":"2015-08-24"},"quote":{"wt":"Intangibles, such as prestige or power, can also represent war aims, though often (albeit not always) their achievement is framed within a more tangible context (e.g. conquest restores prestige, annexation increases power, etc.)."},"date":{"wt":"2014-07-01"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBEU">Fried, Marvin Benjamin (2014-07-01). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=ETDtAwAAQBAJ" id="mwBEY"><i id="mwBEc">Austro-Hungarian War Aims in the Balkans During World War I</i></a>. Palgrave Macmillan (published 2014). p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBEg"> </span>4. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwBEk">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBEo"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/9781137359018" title="Special:BookSources/9781137359018" id="mwBEs">9781137359018</a><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwBEw">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwBE0">2015-08-24</span></span>. <q id="mwBE4">Intangibles, such as prestige or power, can also represent war aims, though often (albeit not always) their achievement is framed within a more tangible context (e.g. conquest restores prestige, annexation increases power, etc.).</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Austro-Hungarian+War+Aims+in+the+Balkans+During+World+War+I&amp;rft.pages=4