r" title="Digital object identifier" id="mwBS4">doi</a>:<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1146%2Fannurev.polisci.1.1.139" id="mwBS8">10.1146/annurev.polisci.1.1.139</a>. Archived from <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://fas-polisci.rutgers.edu/levy/1998%20causes%20of%20war%20%26%20conditions%20of%20peace.pdf" id="mwBTA">the original</a> <span class="cs1-format" id="mwBTE">(PDF)</span> on 2014-10-23.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Annual+Review+of+Political+Science&amp;rft.atitle=The+Causes+of+War+and+the+Conditions+of+Peace&amp;rft.volume=1&amp;rft.pages=139-65&amp;rft.date=1998-06&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev.polisci.1.1.139&amp;rft.aulast=Levy&amp;rft.aufirst=Jack+S.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Ffas-polisci.rutgers.edu%2Flevy%2F1998%2520causes%2520of%2520war%2520%2526%2520conditions%2520of%2520peace.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWar" class="Z3988" about="#mwt444" id="mwBTI"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt444" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwBTM"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-MilitaryAdventurism-127" id="cite_note-MilitaryAdventurism-127"><a href="./War#cite_ref-MilitaryAdventurism_127-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-MilitaryAdventurism-127" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt486" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"year":{"wt":"2001"},"url":{"wt":"http://www.bepress.com/peps/vol7/iss3/3/"},"title":{"wt":"Peace Economics, Peace Science and Public Policy (p. 19)"},"accessdate":{"wt":"2010-02-07"},"deadurl":{"wt":"yes"},"a